  },
  "Factory Rework BCM or CID PAIRING": {
   "width": 9540,
   "height": 9780,
   "color": "rgb(91,105,58)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "FACTORY REWORK : BCM or Customer ID pairing  ",
     "color": "rgb(145,217,147)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 105,
      "top": 15,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 8730
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(173,245,176)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 1560,
      "height": 1245,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Complete the \"APV code\" ( 6 bytes) and press the button \"ENTER REWORK MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(173,245,176)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 165,
      "top": 2070,
      "height": 690,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the REWORK MODE for BCM pairing is launched, then insert a customer ID belonging to the vehicle in the reader",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 105,
      "top": 2805,
      "height": 1065,
      "width": 4410
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Once all the customer IDs are paired, select \"Validate\", and press the button \"EXIT REWORK MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4665,
      "top": 5070,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 4200
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / BCM information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4905,
      "top": 5985,
      "height": 3585,
      "width": 4545
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " CID ANALYSE",
     "color": "rgb(116,174,96)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 90,
      "top": 435,
      "height": 1005,
      "width": 8790
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing information",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 90,
      "top": 7320,
      "height": 2175,
      "width": 4800
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Rework Mode failure ",
     "color": "rgb(240,236,179)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 90,
      "top": 5700,
      "height": 1575,
      "width": 4590
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select \"Standard\" or \"Servant\" and Press the button \"Pairing\" to pair a customer ID or Restricted Access Card",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4650,
      "top": 3750,
      "height": 1335,
      "width": 4200
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the REWORK MODE for customer ID pairing is launched, then insert a customer ID (belonging to the vehicle or blank) in the reader",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 4650,
      "top": 2790,
      "height": 990,
      "width": 4215
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press the button \"BCM pairing\" to pair the BCM",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 3780,
      "height": 825,
      "width": 4395
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) If the BCM is paired, the EXIT of the REWORK MODE is automatic, Then done the pairing of all the customers IDs (procedure in blue)",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4605,
      "height": 690,
      "width": 4395
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    }
   ],
   "presend": [
    {
     "Delay": "0",
     "RequestName": "Start Diagnostic Session.extendedDiagnostic"
    }
